"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-09-tebogo-delivers-olympic-glory-africa-late-mother\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - Letsile Tebogo has always said an Olympic medal would not just be for Botswana but the continent of Africa and he duly delivered on Thursday by becoming the first African to be crowned 200m Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.47905244161061317, \"rank\": 0.5823474422735176, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9975382460232072, \"rank\": 0.0024678255415771354, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 36}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 53, \"to\": 69}, {\"ngram\": \"the continent\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 162}, {\"ngram\": \"the first African\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 192}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old produced a stunning run in Paris to leave pre-race favourite Noah Lyles trailing in third.\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995291091, \"rank\": 4.708886641809724e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stunning run\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, Tebogo is only the second athlete from Africa to even win a medal in the 200m.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"only the second athlete\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Namibian Frankie Fredericks had blazed the way for Tebogo by winning the second of his two silvers in Atlanta in 1996.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999433155451263, \"rank\": 5.668687408108583e-05, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Namibian Frankie Fredericks\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"the second\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"his two silvers\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo set an African record of 19.46sec in the Stade de France to put the cherry on the cake.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"an African record\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"the cherry\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"the cake\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Africans were known for the long distance, marathon, and quarter-mile,\\\" Tebogo toldNBCearlier this year.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Africans\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"the long distance\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"quarter-mile\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"toldNBCearlier\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wanted to change that role and make sure that [people know] Africans can be sprinters too.\\\"\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that role\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"Africans\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"sprinters\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo is proud of his background and listens to traditional Botswanan songs prior to races.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"his background\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional Botswanan songs\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also operates on a set of strong principles.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a set\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"strong principles\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Respect and dedication to what you do,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[It's important] to show people how the culture is.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not throw away the culture, and then adopt the city life.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the city life\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep on pushing the culture so that people can [see] what you are really made of.\\\"\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo's Olympic achievement is even more impressive having been very hard-hit by the death of his greatest fan, beloved mother Seratiwa, in May.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo's Olympic achievement\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"the death\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"his greatest fan\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"beloved mother Seratiwa\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His mother had faithfully followed her son around, slipping into Budapest without Tebogo knowing to watch him become the first male Botswanan athlete to win world championship medals last year.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.999999969023293, \"rank\": 3.05477166637646e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His mother\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"her son\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"the first male Botswanan athlete\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"world championship medals\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are many moments that stand out!\\\"\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many moments\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she toldTheVoiceBWin May this year, just days before her sudden death.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sudden death\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For him to be the first Motswana to raise the blue, black and white flag in short sprints in Kenya 2021 takes centre stage, as does being the first Botswana man to medal at the World Championships last year, and breaking the 200m African record, which stood for over 27 years.\\\"\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.999999356210972, \"rank\": 6.437894995977105e-07, \"text\": \"Motswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.999043396857698, \"rank\": 0.0008988398902719869, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1849, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9975382460232072, \"rank\": 0.0024678255415771354, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the blue, black and white flag\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"short sprints\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"centre stage\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"medal\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m African record\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1945}, {\"ngram\": \"over 27 years\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't always easy for the single mum to handle Tebogo, as well as a daughter who is nine years younger.\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the single mum\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"a daughter\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Letsile has always been a hyperactive child,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Letsile\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"a hyperactive child\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd be chopping veggies and he'd be hiding under the table picking them then eating them raw.\\\"\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"veggies\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo gave up his first sporting love, football, as he did not take well to being substituted.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"his first sporting love\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Tebogo also realised if he became an athlete there was a better chance of him being \\\"able to put food on the family's table\\\" and repay his mother for all her sacrifices.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"a better chance\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"the family's table\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"his mother\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"all her sacrifices\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless as he grew up with his extended family he still had to train for athletics and play football without shoes - he toldNBC\\\"everything had to be equal.\\\"\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his extended family\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"shoes\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He called his mother his \\\"rock\\\" - and she did everything for her son.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his mother\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"rock\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"her son\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Putting my interests on hold and emptying my savings just to be with him,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my interests\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2784}, {\"ngram\": \"my savings\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Note that our relationship is more than that of mother and son, we are more brother and sister now - more so that, for the longest time, it was just me and him.\\\"\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our relationship\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"mother\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"son\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"more brother\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"sister\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"the longest time\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She provided stability off the track while his coach Kebonyemodisa 'Dose' Mosimanyane provided it in his athletics career.\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stability\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3062}, {\"ngram\": \"Kebonyemodisa\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"'Dose' Mosimanyane\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"his athletics career\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it was mum who ruled the roost in almost every respect.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mum\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"the roost\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3173}, {\"ngram\": \"almost every respect\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is the boy next door,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boy\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You should see him at the cattlepost doing everything any Motswana child does.\\\"\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3297, \"end\": 3305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.999999356210972, \"rank\": 6.437894995977105e-07, \"text\": \"Motswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cattlepost\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless she had bought a new car this year for his birthday - giving it to him early as he was to leave for a meet.\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new car\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"a meet\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her death left him bereft.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her death\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does not even feel like my birthday anymore.\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my birthday\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think I will enjoy it anymore,\\\" Tebogo posted on social media.\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3566}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of all, she was not there to see her boy crowned Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her boy\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3637}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3680}]}]}"